  "textPreview": "Enroll in our free AI Search Toolkit course and future-proof your search visibility\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nAnswer Engine Optimization Checker\n\nGet full visibility into your presence across top answer engines. Analyze brand mentions, benchmark visibility, and monitor competitors with our AEO Checker Tool\n\nBrand\nDomain\nCountry\nUnited States\n\nYou have 5 free checks left for today\n\nRun a free check\nCheck your brand’s visibility across major answer engines\n\nKnow what LLMs say about you and your competitors. Get accurate data on mentions, links, prompts, and check historical data with SE Ranking’s top answer engine optimization software\n\nChatGPT\nAI Mode\nPerplexity\nGemini\nChatGPT\n\nFind out if and how ChatGPT features your brand in its answers. Monitor links and mentions, check the prompts, and compare your presence to competitors.\n\nStart free trial\nControl your brand narrative in AI answers and build winning strategies with visibility analytics!\nTry now\nSolve real challenges with our AEO Tool\n\nTackle major AEO bottlenecks with one of the best answer engine optimization solutions. Our tool is designed to help you track, compare, and improve your visibility.\n\nReview AI answers to your queries\n\nSee how AI engines respond to your target prompts. Check answers for quality, accuracy, and brand strategy alignment.\n\nTrack your brand mentions and links\n\nMonitor your brand mentions and links across AI answer engines. Stay in control of your presence and never miss a citation.\n\nBenchmark against your competitors\n\nCompare and analyze competitor AI presence against yours to identify who’s winning and where you can outperform them.\n\nAnalyze your AI positions\n\nCheck how your brand ranks within AI answers. Spot opportunities to improve your placement for maximum impact.\n\nStart Free Trial\nAutomate and scale your answer engine optimization\n\nLearn about, monitor, and improve your AI visibility based on accurate data and smart insights. St",
